      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Paid time Off",
      "fontSize": 25.590890892905698,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Paid time Off",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FAQkV1JAxx0C6-XfH9f46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -478.78008300648617,
      "y": 5905.807305584477,
      "width": 906.9639159170658,
      "height": 120.50898601783372,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bvx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2011694818,
      "version": 1083,
      "versionNonce": 307223172,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1762506125393,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Employees can view only their own time off records, while\nAdmins and HR Officers can view time off records &\napprove/reject them for all employees",
      "fontSize": 32.13572960475566,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Employees can view only their own time off records, while Admins and HR Officers can view time off records &\napprove/reject them for all employees",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WTPZF_1dlByYw1mQQvhQK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2733.1590705366325,
      "y": 7383.225726446396,
      "width": 797.0576782226562,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bvy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1597188706,
      "version": 417,
      "versionNonce": 1016280580,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1762497492051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Payroll Dashboard contains warnings, pay run information, and statistics\nrelated to employee and employer costs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Payroll Dashboard contains warnings, pay run information, and statistics related to employee and employer costs",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wHmcxGKEd9yx9f2i97NIm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1612.8644029747838,
      "y": 7394.589348213299,
      "width": 1034.34765625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bvz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1491791010,
      "version": 473,
      "versionNonce": 474338692,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1762497492051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The Payroll Payrun allows you to generate payslips for all employees at once. When you click the Payrun\nbutton, all employee payslips are created automatically.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The Payroll Payrun allows you to generate payslips for all employees at once. When you click the Payrun button, all employee payslips are created automatically.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7f1ripM3dRgHedZQJlokR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -326.0896285142171,
      "y": 7310.996319009429,
      "width": 799.585693359375,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bw0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 99137826,
      "version": 425,
      "versionNonce": 997754116,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1762497492051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When a user opens any generated payslip, they can view detailed information such\nas working days and worked day amounts. They can also generate a new payslip\nor cancel , and they can print the payslip as well.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When a user opens any generated payslip, they can view detailed information such as working days and worked day amounts. They can also generate a new payslip or cancel , and they can print the payslip as well.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uYsMP3MUjbLJQ5_KYHuaz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 789.3913764732251,
      "y": 7296.104544549266,
      "width": 872.6262817382817,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bw1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 463572002,
      "version": 478,
      "versionNonce": 1336493188,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1762497492051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Users can also view the payslip computation, which shows how the total amount is calculated from different\nsalary heads, including allowances and deductions.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Users can also view the payslip computation, which shows how the total amount is calculated from different salary heads, including allowances and deductions.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
