      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- In the Admin Settings, the administrator can assign user access rights based on each\nuser’s role.\n- Access rights can be configured on an module basis, allowing specific permissions for each\nmodule.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- In the Admin Settings, the administrator can assign user access rights based on each user’s role.\n- Access rights can be configured on an module basis, allowing specific permissions for each module.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
