      "updated": 1762495838296,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Normal user cannot register, so when the HR officer\nor Admin creates a new user/employee, there ID should\nalso be created with this method.\n\n- There password should be auto generated for the\nfirst time by the system.\n\n-They can login and change the system generated\npassword.",
      "fontSize": 21.185185185185194,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Normal user cannot register, so when the HR officer or Admin creates a new user/employee, there ID should also be created with this method.\n\n- There password should be auto generated for the first time by the system.\n\n-They can login and change the system generated password.",
      "autoResize": false,
